<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span><span class="c4">[بَطُؤَ]</span>، مهموز،<span class="c5"> بُطْئاً:</span> أي أبطأ.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
